  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/f6aa56dad7cbbbea8aa2db84e982ec4f.poster.avif?t=1769851755\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/f6aa56dad7cbbbea8aa2db84e982ec4f.webm?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/f6aa56dad7cbbbea8aa2db84e982ec4f.mp4?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You have the gift of navigating the nightmares of the deceased to uncover how they died. You're not the only one.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/d3fc0e160a180c701fc1ebf8e8900f0b.poster.avif?t=1769851755\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/d3fc0e160a180c701fc1ebf8e8900f0b.webm?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/d3fc0e160a180c701fc1ebf8e8900f0b.mp4?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Through an ancient talisman, followers of \"The Eye Syndicate\" can possess the innocent and abuse them for their extreme ritual interests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you set yourself free from this horrifying nightmare? Will you free the victim of Case 37's possessed soul, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or will you be forever trapped, allowing \"The Eye Syndicate\" to possess you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only you can decide the fate of Vera Herdman, The gifted detective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/6816948f8787dc9438e63186b01673c4.poster.avif?t=1769851755\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/6816948f8787dc9438e63186b01673c4.webm?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/6816948f8787dc9438e63186b01673c4.mp4?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>MASSIVE UPDATES   <br>   </strong></u>- There is always room for improvement and expansion. Out of love to the story the game has received 15 major/minor updates regularly. More content has been added to delve deeper into the story and explore additional dimensions of the nightmare.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/f6aa56dad7cbbbea8aa2db84e982ec4f.poster.avif?t=1769851755\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/f6aa56dad7cbbbea8aa2db84e982ec4f.webm?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/f6aa56dad7cbbbea8aa2db84e982ec4f.mp4?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You have the gift of navigating the nightmares of the deceased to uncover how they died. You're not the only one.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/d3fc0e160a180c701fc1ebf8e8900f0b.poster.avif?t=1769851755\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/d3fc0e160a180c701fc1ebf8e8900f0b.webm?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/d3fc0e160a180c701fc1ebf8e8900f0b.mp4?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Through an ancient talisman, followers of \"The Eye Syndicate\" can possess the innocent and abuse them for their extreme ritual interests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you set yourself free from this horrifying nightmare? Will you free the victim of Case 37's possessed soul, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or will you be forever trapped, allowing \"The Eye Syndicate\" to possess you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only you can decide the fate of Vera Herdman, The gifted detective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/6816948f8787dc9438e63186b01673c4.poster.avif?t=1769851755\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/6816948f8787dc9438e63186b01673c4.webm?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709220/extras/6816948f8787dc9438e63186b01673c4.mp4?t=1769851755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>MASSIVE UPDATES   <br>   </strong></u>- There is always room for improvement and expansion. Out of love to the story the game has received 15 major/minor updates regularly. More content has been added to delve deeper into the story and explore additional dimensions of the nightmare.</p>",
